Source code/PPA: https://launchpad.net/~mir-team/+archive/staging

Add to /etc/pacman.conf above all other repos (repo from: https://wiki.archlinux.org/index.php/AMD_Catalyst#Xorg_repositories):

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
[xorg113]
SigLevel = Optional TrustAll
Server = http://catalyst.wirephire.com/repo/xorg113/$arch
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Downgrade to Xorg 1.13.*

--------------------------------------------------------------------------------
sudo pacman -Sy $(pacman -Q | grep -E '(xorg-server|xf86-input|xf86-video)(-)?.*' | cut -d' ' -f1)
--------------------------------------------------------------------------------

Install the packages

* mesa-mir
* gflags
* mir-bzr
* glmark2-mir-bzr
* runbench-bzr
* xorg-server-mir
* xf86-video-intel-mir-bzr
* xf86-video-nouveau-mir-bzr
* tslib
* sdl2-mir
* unity-system-compositor-bzr
* lightdm-mir-bzr

* qt5-3d-git
* qt5-jsondb-git
* qt5-location-git
